ALL THE FOLLOWING TESTS ARE DESIGNED TO BE EXECUTED USING
THE SANDIA-SST SIMULATOR.  THEY REQUIRE THE USE OF THE
SST-ELEMENTS PACKAGE 6.0.0+.  PAY SPECIAL ATTENTION TO THE
INDIVIDUAL RELEASE DIRECTORIES AS EACH OF THE TEST
DIRECTORIES IS TAILORED TO THE SPECIFIC SST RELEASE.

GIVEN THAT THE ORIGINAL TESTS WERE DERIVED FROM
EXISTING SST TESTS, WE MAINTAIN THE ORIGINAL SANDIA
LICENSE TERMS.  SEE 'LICENSE' FOR MORE DETAILS.

